#: templates/welcome.html:245
msgid "FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS"
msgstr "常见问题"

#: templates/welcome.html:248
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                What is %(QWIK)sGAME?\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                什么是 %(QWIK)sGAME？\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:255
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME is an app which facilitates finding "
"partners and arranging 2-player games.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME 是一款帮助寻找伙伴并安排双人游戏的应用程"
"序。\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:262
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                For which games can I find partners on %(QWIK)sGAME?\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                我可以在 %(QWIK)sGAME 上为哪些游戏寻找伙伴？\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:269
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME focuses on 2-player games only with "
"ambitious plans for multi-player games in the future. Currently we have the "
"most popular 2-player games like tennis, squash, table tennis, badminton, "
"racquetball, but also chess, darts, backgammon, billiards and more.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME 目前专注于双人游戏，并计划在未来扩展到多人游"
"戏。目前涵盖最受欢迎的双人游戏，如网球、壁球、乒乓球、羽毛球、回力球，以及国"
"际象棋、飞镖、西洋双陆棋、台球等。\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:276
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                Is %(QWIK)sGAME paid?\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                %(QWIK)sGAME 需要付费吗？\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:283
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME is free of charge.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME 完全免费。\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:290
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                Is %(QWIK)sGAME available in my country?\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                %(QWIK)sGAME 在我的国家可以使用吗？\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:297
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME works anywhere in the world.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME 在全球任何地方都可以使用。\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:304
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                How do I find partner and schedule a match with "
"%(QWIK)sGAME?\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                我如何使用 %(QWIK)sGAME 寻找伙伴并安排比赛？\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:311
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    To find a partner and organize a match start by sending "
"an invitation for a match. Select the game, venue and a timeframe. It is "
"recommended to call the venue and check if there are available playgrounds "
"for your preferred timeframe. Your Match Invitation will be visible in the "
"QWIKFeed to other Players. Multiple Players may respond to your Invitation. "
"You get to choose the best offer and confirm the match. You can also reply "
"to an existing invitation from the %(QWIK)sFeed by placing an offer for a "
"particular hour from the given timeframe.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    要寻找伙伴并组织比赛，请先发送一条比赛邀请。选择游戏、场"
"地和时间段。建议提前联系场地确认在您首选时间是否有可用场地。您的比赛邀请将显"
"示在 QWIKFeed 中供其他玩家查看。可能会有多位玩家回应您的邀请。您可以选择最合"
"适的报价并确认比赛。您也可以在 %(QWIK)sFeed 中回复现有邀请，为指定时间段内的"
"某个具体小时提交报价。\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:318
msgid ""
"\n"
"                How many invitations can I send?\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                我可以发送多少个邀请？\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:325
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    You can post as many invitations as you wish every day "
"and for any game, venue or timeframe.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    您每天可以根据需要发布任意数量的邀请，适用于任何游戏、场"
"地或时间段。\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:332
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                What is %(QWIK)sFeed?\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                什么是 %(QWIK)sFeed？\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:339
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    You can find all current invitations in our "
"%(QWIK)sFeed. It is contantly updated with new invitations sent by Players.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    您可以在 %(QWIK)sFeed 中查看所有当前邀请。该页面会持续更"
"新玩家发布的新邀请。\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:346
msgid ""
"\n"
"                Who books the court/playground?\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                谁负责预订场地？\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:353
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    The Player who send the initial match invitation is "
"responsible to call and book a court/playground once the match is confirmed. "
"The Player is also recommended to call and check the venue availability "
"before sending the invitation.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    发送最初比赛邀请的玩家在比赛确认后负责联系并预订场地。同"
"时建议在发送邀请前先致电场地确认可用情况。\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:360
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                Why can't I find %(QWIK)sGAME in the PlayStore and "
"AppStore?\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                为什么我在 PlayStore 和 AppStore 找不到 %(QWIK)sGAME？\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:367
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME is a Progressive Web App. It's the new "
"generation of apps. No need to download nor install anything. Just save "
"%(QWIK)sGAME on your Home screen. %(QWIK)sGAME PWA works on all operating "
"systems and an Internet Browser is the only requirement.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME 是一款渐进式网页应用（PWA），属于新一代应用"
"形式。无需下载或安装任何内容。只需将 %(QWIK)sGAME 保存到您的主屏幕即"
"可。%(QWIK)sGAME PWA 可在所有操作系统上运行，仅需互联网浏览器。\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:374
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                Who owns %(QWIK)sGAME?\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                谁拥有 %(QWIK)sGAME？\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:381
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME is managed by QWIKGAME Inc. registered in "
"Victoria, Australia as a Not For Profit Association. All discussions and "
"decisions regarding %(QWIK)sGAME are made online in the <a href=\"https://"
"forum.qwikgame.org/\" target=\"_blank\">QWIK Forum</a>. Your assistance will "
"be most welcome.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    %(QWIK)sGAME 由 QWIKGAME Inc. 管理，该机构注册于澳大利亚"
"维多利亚州，为非营利协会。关于 %(QWIK)sGAME 的所有讨论和决策均在 <a "
"href=\"https://forum.qwikgame.org/\" target=\"_blank\">QWIK Forum</a> 在线进"
"行。欢迎您的参与和支持。\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:388
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                Is %(QWIK)sGAME open-source?\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                %(QWIK)sGAME 是开源的吗？\n"

#: templates/welcome.html:395
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    Yes! The %(QWIK)sGAME software is entirely open-source. "
"The latest code can be found on %(github_link)s. Your assistance will be "
"most welcome.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    是的！%(QWIK)sGAME 软件完全开源。最新代码可在 "
"%(github_link)s 上获取。欢迎您的参与和贡献。\n"

